This is another jQuery Placeholder plugin, but this one is enhanced.

What this plugin does:

- Cross-browser placeholder html5 attribute
- Styling color of placeholder text in all browser, but letting native placeholder focus/blur event if supported



What's next:

- Code organize to easily customize settings
- Add support for password input type
- May be check if the browser supports native css styling:

/* webkit */
::-webkit-input-placeholder { color:#999 }

/* mozilla */
:-moz-placeholder { color: #999 }